snippet.title: TS:NONUPLE NINE - Anime PV and Footage
snippet.description:
Science is falling in love with a truth forever beyond your reach.

A huge monitor and a lone chair. You, the "observer", are confined to this room. There is no exit.
On the monitor is the "subject" - a girl with no memories.
A floating drone conveys her every move to you.
If you cannot reclaim the girl's memories, then both your lives will be forfeit.

A wide range of animated scenes and effects draw you into the story. If you're not careful you might end up joining the ranks of those unwittingly playing until sunrise!
